room_title: Escape room "Treacherous Treasures" by Creative Escape in Muldrow
room_description: A world renown, highly respected but deeply envied explorer has found some of the greatest treasures ever seen. He has recently gone missing without a trace. It may not be safe for long, so use your time wisely. Can you find his most prized discovery? Or will you fall into the treachery that surrounds these treasures?
